"On a regular basis, excises need to be declared. To support you with this "
"duty, a report generated weekly provides the quantity by excise category "
"entering and exiting your fiscal deposit warehouse with a dedicated activity "
"for it."
msgstr ""

#. module: micro_brewery
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:micro_brewery.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"On top of all the reporting you can find in the different applications, you "
"can consult the dashboard application to follow the volume of Sales you have "
"made."
msgstr ""
"Pe lângă toate rapoartele disponibile în diferite aplicații, poți consulta "
"aplicația de tablouri de bord pentru a urmări volumul vânzărilor realizate."

#. module: micro_brewery
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:micro_brewery.welcome_article_body
